room_title: Escape room "Alcatraz" by Hourglass Escape Rooms in Russellville
room_description:
Your crew has been thrown into the pen, but luck may be on your side. The last prisoner in your cell successfully escaped, can you follow the clues he left behind and escape as well? You only have one hour until the guards walk their next rounds.
